Utrecht is a city in the Netherlands, known for its medieval center. It has tree-lined canals, Christian monuments and a venerable university. It is the fourth-largest city and a municipality of the Netherlands 🇳🇱 
Have you been to Utrecht before? 🤍
Courtesy of @utrechtalive
